this is list of localdb commands available:

localdb init "foldername"
    set the folder which all databases are stored in local system
    example:
        localdb init /home/user/DecenDB

localdb new "database name"
    creates a new database if database already exists returns error 
    example:
        local new mydatabase

localdb drop "database name"
    delete database return error if database already deosn't exists
    example:
        localdb drop mydatabase

localdb show
    show list of databases

